DaLastAlert 3
*************

Introduction
============

   Are you tired of always having troubles with finding your pen and
paper just to write down the last guru you got?  Now this problem is
solved because I have written a 'small' and quick program that will
show not only the last guru, but also a nice hint to what caused it!

   If you don't get the point of what this program can be used to then
try to read the section @{"What AS wrote about LA2" Link "What AS wrote about LA2"}.


@EndNode

